(a - b)^{2} \leq 3a^{2} + 3b^{2}
(a - b)^{2} \leq K(a^{2} + b^{2})
K < 3
\color{red}{\mathbf 2}\cdot(a^2+b^2)-(a-b)^2=(a+b)^2\geqslant0
0\le(a+b)^{2}=a^2+b^2+2ab \implies -2ab\le a^2+b^2,
(a-b)^{2}=a^2+b^2-2ab\le 2a^2+2b^2.
K\ge2
b=-a\ne0
K=2
Ka^2+Kb^2-(a-b)^2=(K-1)a^2+2ab+(K-1)b^2=(a+b)^2+(K-2)(a^2+b^2)\ge0
